<title>
DTC P0649
</title>
<servinfosub id = "ASLAP70AA104009001">
<title>
Podmienky rozoznania DTC a problémová oblasť
</title>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "4.981in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "2.227in"/>
<thead>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Podmienky rozoznania DTC
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Problémová oblasť
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
<emph etype = "bold">
DTC P0649: Riadiaci obvod kontrolky rýchlosti
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Kontrolka CRUISE / SET a jej signál zo združeného merača sa nezmení, aj keď ECM vysiela požiadavku na zapnutie alebo vypnutie kontrolky CRUISE / SET do združeného merača cez komunikáciu CAN.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Komunikačný obvod CAN
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Združený merač
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
ECM
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "ASLAP70AA104009002">
<title>
Riešenie problémov DTC
</title>
<diag type = "test" id = "ASLAP70AA104009003">
<testgroup id = "ASLAP70AA104009004">
<title>
Kontrola DTC
</title>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Skontrolujte riadiace jednotky komunikujúce prostredníctvom CAN, či nemajú DTC.
</ptxt>
</test1>
<question>
Našli ste nejaké CAN-DTC?
</question>
<result type = "yes"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Pokračujte príslušným postupom riešenia DTC. 
</ptxt>
</action>
<result type = "no"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Vymeňte združený merač a opätovne skontrolujte DTC. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "ASLAP70A9306001"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
 Ak je detekovaná DTC P0649 opätovne, vymeňte ECM a opätovne skontrolujte DTC. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "ASLAP70A1306001"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</action>
</testgroup>
</diag>
</servinfosub>
</servinfo>
